stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CatalogInvalid: 事务 1：创建目录项
    CatalogInvalid --> WaitWriters1: indisvalid=false
    WaitWriters1 --> BuildScan: 等待可能写表的旧事务
    BuildScan --> ReadyForWrites: 第一次 Heap 扫描并构建
    ReadyForWrites --> WaitWriters2: 新写入开始维护索引
    WaitWriters2 --> ValidateScan: 第二次 Heap 扫描验证遗漏 Tuple
    ValidateScan --> WaitOldSnapshots: 等待早于第二次扫描的 Snapshot
    WaitOldSnapshots --> Valid: indisvalid=true
    Valid --> [*]
    CatalogInvalid --> FailedInvalid: 错误/取消
    BuildScan --> FailedInvalid
    ValidateScan --> FailedInvalid
